column1: Regular traffic reports will resume Friday December 13 at 4:00 p.m.

column3: TRAFFIC ALERT FOR US-68 IN JESSAMINE CO:
column4: Roadway down to one lane in each direction.  Serious multi-vehicle collision about 1.5 miles from the Fayette Co line.  Traffic reportedly diverted to the emergency lanes.

column3: TRAFFIC ALERT FOR US-68 IN JESSAMINE CO:
column4: Expect significant delays during rush hour or seek an alternate route if possible.
